:"由点连成线，形成T型认识，有自己的深度也有一定的广度。然后结合业务提升技术，技术反哺业务，形成自己的面。然后结合时代大背景，找到一个体，然后驾航远行。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":172072,"user_name":"孙磊","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1007185,"ip_address":"","ucode":"F2EB22676A2B80","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/5e/51/82d64610.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1579082507,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1579082507","product_id":100012101,"comment_content":"可能我天生愚钝，点，线明白他们之间的关系，面，我的理解是你从事的业务领域可能存在多条线，比如一个系统至少开发，和自动化测试就是两条线，是不是建立起一个面，就是把你所在的业务领域的各条线理清楚。所以面其实还是业务领域驱动的。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":139430,"user_name":"丁丁历险记","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1661704,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A43829E454C067","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/5b/08/b0b0db05.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1570631517,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1570631517","product_id":100012101,"comment_content":"没python...","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":112599,"user_name":"kevin","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1199192,"ip_address":"","ucode":"918EFC033B1630","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/4c/58/25152fa9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1562768575,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1562768575","product_id":100012101,"comment_content":"T型发展路线有借鉴意义，点线面体的思考行程自己的体系","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":47086,"user_name":"北风一叶","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1087302,"ip_address":"","ucode":"30310E66341D2A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/97/46/fe1f21d8.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1544054601,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"16855","content":"加油💪","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"mindwind","uid":"1001723","ctime":1544094026,"ip_address":"","comment_id":47086,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"154405